title: Tired of Aimlessly searching for a place!?
posting_body: Are you tired of searching aimlessly online for a place?
If you answered yes to any one of those questions you need to call/text me now!
I work to find folks Houses/Condos  and apartments in Austin and surrounding and would love to be your agent on your next home!
My service is FREE folks, and I work with integrity with all my clients as a fiduciary.
If you pick up that 1000 pound phone and give me a call/text, you just saved yourself anxiety, panic, and home search depression!
Look forward to helping you with all your housing needs!
(Wow this could be a prescription drug commercial LOL)
to inquiry on my FREE service--
–Let me know your budget, ideal location, and move in date in the text!--
–Expect the BEST service, because that is what you deserve–
--Scott Petermann--HomeSmith Realty--Austin Board of Realtors--10 year Veteran–
